Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
57 Berwick Street is a quality B-Grade building situated in the heart of Fortitude Valley. Located seconds from award winning cafes, restaurants and the renowned James Street precinct, the property offers staff amenity which is second to none. The property has easy access to the CBD and is easily accessible by all forms of public transport; the Fortitude Valley Train Station is only a five minute walk away.

The tenancy can offer space from 285sqm up to 700sqm. The space is fitted out with multiple offices, boardroom, training room, meeting room and open plan work areas. The property offers large outdoor balcony spaces and internal BBQ areas with fresh air. A side core allows for ultimate efficiencies in the lay out of the floor and a central ceiling void allows for great natural light penetration. 

Key Features:
-  Ample onsite secure car parking
-  Quality building with availability from 300-700msqm
-  Disabled access  
-  Competitive rental and flexible terms on offer
-  Dual bathrooms and kitchen break out space 

For more information or to arrange an inspection, please contact Exclusive Agents.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Onsite parking and only 350m from train

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
The Bread Factory precinct is a campus-style office accommodation opportunity for progressive businesses who value a unique workplace and staff wellness. The precinct is linked by a variety of lane-way style outdoor spaces, allowing for staff breakout and easy access in all directions.
  
Highlights of the precinct include:
  
  -  Ample onsite car parking
  -  350m from Fortitude Valley Train Station (which offers direct access to all lines)
  -  End of Trip facilities (showers and bike racks)
  -  Endless staff amenity easily accessible including Richmont Hotel, Valley Metro retail precinct (Woolworths Metro, etc) and FV by Gurner's large restaurant offering
  -  Various communal meeting spaces and external upgrades to be delivered by Q3 2021
  
  
The current vacancies are across two separate buildings being:
  
KEATING'S BREAD FACTORY
Built in 1916, Keating's Bread Factory is a stunning heritage building that has been refurbished and restored to it's original design. Featuring exposed brick, wooden beams and even the original bread ovens; the tenancy is unique and is now available to be leased.
This building currently offers a 277sqm tenancy with an existing fitout in place, including two meeting rooms and open plan work stations.
  
KENNIGO SUITES
The Kennigo Suites are perfectly designed for smaller businesses and start-ups, accommodating 33-100sqm. Each suite has its own amenities, shopfront and can be fitted out to suit your requirements.
  
  
For more information on the opportunity, please contact the Exclusive Agents listed below.

CBRE on behalf of the Landlords are pleased to bring to market for lease 757 Ann Street, Fortitude Valley. A premium A Grade building constructed in 2014.

  -  400-2,200sqm fitted out contiguous office
  -  Exceptional natural light and panoramic views
  -  Onsite bars and restaurants
  -  End of Trip facilities
  -  4.5 Star NABERS Energy Rating

Situated in the heart of Fortitude Valley, 757 Ann Street has direct access to cafes, restaurants, bars and has easy access to the James Street precinct, Emporium and HQ retail centres. Fortitude Valley Train Station is a five minute walk away and bus stops are at your doorstep.

For further information or to arrange an inspection, contact your Exclusive Marketing Agents CBRE.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: A world first in sustainable design
Home to global engineering firm Aurecon

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
In the heart of the Brisbane Showgrounds, Lendlease is developing Queensland’s first engineered timber office building to be delivered Q4 2018. Located just five minutes from the CBD, this $2.9 billion redevelopment is capturing the soul of the area’s rich heritage to create a workplace without boundaries.

25 King’s innovative design and timber construction contribute an architectural statement to the fabric of King Street. Prefabricated timber floors, columns and beams complement high ceilings and striking windows, bringing the nature of the forest into your workspace. With state-of-the-art technology and sustainable outcomes, 25 King is the definition of a connected, collaborative workspace for high-performance teams.

Make an impact and discover your future workplace

-	817sqm Turn Key Office 
-	High quality fit out in place 
-	Fully Refurbished Building 
-	Competitive effective rental on offer 
-	5 Star NABERS Rating 
-	Brand New End of Trip Facilities 

Situated in the heart of Fortitude Valley, just seconds from the James Street precinct, is the opportunity to secure an 817sqm fully fitted out A Grade office. The available space has been designed to accommodate up to 100 staff. Set across half a floor plate, the tenancy has been fitted out with multiple offices, boardroom, meeting rooms/collaboration areas, reception and workstations set up for 95 staff. 

The building is situated on a prominent corner site and has access to a plethora of retail amenity at your doorstep including HQ, Emporium and James Street all of which are home to award winning cafes, restaurants and bars. The property is easily accessible to all forms of public transport and offers onsite car parking. 

For further information or to arrange an inspection, contact your Exclusive Marketing Agents CBRE.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: PRIME SUBLEASE OPPORTUNITY IN PREMIUM ASSET!

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Close proximity to all public transport

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
HQ South Tower is a premium A-Grade commercial office tower located in the heart of Fortitude Valley. The building offers 6 levels of office accommodation totaling 12,900sqm of nettable area and is serviced by 4 x Kones lifts from basement 2 to level 8 and an additional 1 x lift from basement 2 to level 2. The modern End of Trip facilities is accessible via a separate and safe ground floor ingress off Wickham Street, and features 250 bike spaces, male/female shower rooms and locker access.  

Strategically located at 520 Wickham Street (approx. 1km from the CBD), HQ South Tower is positioned directly across from the prestigious Emporium Complex, a vibrant mixed use development with retail, office, hotel and residential components.  Tenants will enjoy transport offerings available including; rail (400m), bus services (including the City Glider) and a taxi rank at the front door. 

Available Areas: 
Level 2, Suite 2: 252sqm - Partial Fitout
Level 2, Suite 3: 399sqm - Partial Fitout

Building Features: 
• Substantial commercial development perfectly blended with retail and social amenities
• Secure basement car parking at a ratio of 1:80sqm
• 70 visitor car bays - free of charge for 2 hours
• Ground floor cafe
• Highly efficient floor plate design
• End of Trip facilities for 250 bikes & 28 showers
• 5.0-Star Green Star Rating

Please contact Exclusive Agents, CBRE and Knight Frank for more information or to arrange an inspection.
